    <p>This page and the underlying analysis are <b>independent</b>, produced by a Toronto resident. The work is <b>not produced, reviewed, validated, or endorsed by the City of Toronto, Toronto Police Service, the Province of Ontario, or any government body or agency</b>. No causal claim is made about why measured speeds changed; the difference-in-differences method controls for prior-year seasonality but cannot rule out other simultaneous factors.</p>
